title: How to buy a home with only $1500 down! FREE Info!
posting_body: ['Did you know that you can buy a home for as little as $1000 down?', 'My name is Steve.', 'I am a licensed real estate agent here in the twin cities.', 'It is possible to buy a home with very little out of pocket, but it will require good credit.', 'If you have a credit score over 660 and are employed full time ...', 'You may be able to qualify for a 2nd loan to cover the costs needed for down payment.', 'And depending on what County you live in, there are loans and grants available as well.', 'You will need good credit and income.', 'A credit score over 660.', 'A full time job with w2 or 1099 income (preferably 2+ years).', '2 years of tax returns.', 'You will need about $1500 to cover the cost of earnest money and inspection.', 'I created a web page with a form you can fill out to find all of the available down payment assistance programs available to you.', 'Check out my website below:', '<URL>', 'I am a licensed Realtor in the state of MN and WI.', 'Please send me an email with your phone number and email address, and I will respond as soon as possible, you can also call me at:', 'show contact info', '.', 'If your property is now listed with a REALTOR or Broker, please disregard this offer, as it is not our intention to solicit the offerings of other REALTORS or Brokers.']
